Summary: Walking in my back yard when I saw this cigar shape object flying at a low level,going about 15 miles an hour.
divs: sighting detailsi, {pid} saw this cigar shaped object flying over my house while i was walking around in my back yard. the object circle around my house for about 15 to 20 minutes. it was flashing light blue and bright orange colors. it must have been around 50 to 75 yards long ( roughly speeking). it made no sound but after 15 to 20 minutes it flu off at the speed of light, not making any kind of sound. my nabor called and stated they saw it too! for how long i don't know. this is not the first time i saw a ufo object in my area. {cms\jat\pid} text moved to narrative
